  "body": "Since the IPC is a standardised (or becoming) we should store this in a shared folder so that both `eth` and `geth` can benefit from the same location.\n\nShared FDs should go to `~/.ethereum/shared`. The FD should be renamed from `geth.ipc` to simply `ipc`.\n",
