    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The default on Windows is `\\\\.\\pipe\\geth.ipc`. We can change that to `\\\\.\\pipe\\ethereum`. I would suggest to use `${datadir}/shared/ethereum.sock` as the default name for the unix socket endpoint. According to [FHS](http://www.pathname.com/fhs/pub/fhs-2.3.html) we should place them in `/var/run`. But this requires root permissions and gives conflicts when multiple clients are run on the same machine and all want to have the same endpoint.\n",
